DPO1_ECOLI - Also known as resA. Experimental evidence at protein level: Swiss-Prot protein existence level 1. In addition to polymerase activity, this DNA polymerase exhibits 3'-5' and 5'-3' exonuclease activity. It is able to utilize nicked circular duplex DNA as a template and can unwind the parental DNA strand from its template. From Escherichia coli (strain K12).
